reviewText:
Playboy / Spring Break is fifty-five minutes and was released on video on February 18, 1997. This is the sequel (if you want to call it that) to the Girls of Spring Break. Featured are eight beautiful college students who are knock out with or with out clothes. When not focusing on the ladies, we are treated to mini clips of beautiful babes parting and having a good time. Here in the order that they appear are the college co-eds.

Brandi V-Takes forever to take the dress off and when it does, the camera operator does not do a very good job showing her nude.
Haven, Brandi C, and Gladamyer-All three start out wearing two piece bikinis by the poolside and Brandi is the first to go topless then completely nude. The other two are just topless.
Dafney & Elizabeth-The two start off wearing lingerie and eventually Elizabeth becomes topless and then Dafney. Both of the ladies become nude.
Victoria-Strips in front of a horse
Robyn-Nude on a haystack
Antoinette-Becomes completely nude while Brandi V hoses her down and she too becomes nude
Haven, Brandi C, and Gladamyer-All three are nude in and out of the lake and on a car
Ashley-Totally nude by the poolside
Christine-Starts off wearing a two piece bikini and quickly becomes fully nude
All eight become nude in the car wash segment

This is really a great video to own. Playboy / Spring Break get an AAAAA+++++.
